{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Handles push notification registration failure.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"error","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Log the error for debugging","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Retry registration if appropriate"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update device status in the Control Panel"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistrationFailure:":{"title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Handles push notification registration failure.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol"}}}